```console
$ ghdash --help
Dashboard for Github account

Usage: ghdash [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -v, --verbose...
          More output per occurrence

  -q, --quiet...
          Less output per occurrence

  -c, --config <CONFIG>
          Force the calculation of the version number alternate configuration file

  -u, --user <USER>
          github user name

  -t, --token <TOKEN>
          github personal access token

  -r, --repositories <REPOSITORIES>
          scope for the repositories shown in the dashboard

          Possible values:
          - authored: Public repositories that are original written by the user
          - forked:   Public repositories that are forked from other authors
          - public:   All public repositories
          - private:  All private repositories

  -h, --help
          Print help information (use `-h` for a summary)

  -V, --version
          Print version information

```

